--/ Domains

--| A _system domain_ represents the extent to which a single legal entity (an individual or an 
--| organisation) has jurisdiction over a set of computer equipment, the software running on it, 
--| and the data stored within it. 

    type System_Domain is abstract limited tagged private;

    type Domain_Access is access all System_Domain'Class;

